                placeholder={`Paste your data here (Excel copy/paste or CSV).\n\nParsing Rules:\n1. The LAST 2 columns are Model A and Model B.\n2. Any columns immediately preceding the models that are URLs are Reference Images.\n3. Everything else to the left is combined as the Prompt.\n\nSupport: "Quotes, with, commas", Tabs, or standard CSV.`}
                value={inputText}
